751
00:50:20,351 --> 00:50:22,228
Despachem-se e tragam-no para cima!

752
00:50:22,311 --> 00:50:24,647
Mais! Sim!

753
00:50:30,319 --> 00:50:31,153
Isto...

754
00:50:32,363 --> 00:50:35,824
Salvámos isto!

755
00:50:36,325 --> 00:50:37,868
Acabámos de o salvar!

756
00:50:37,952 --> 00:50:39,870
Ena.

757
00:50:44,542 --> 00:50:45,960
Não tem de vir.

758
00:50:47,920 --> 00:50:49,129
Já chegou.

759
00:51:09,275 --> 00:51:10,109
<i>In-pyo.</i>

760
00:51:10,776 --> 00:51:12,069
<i>Já estão a terminar.</i>

761
00:51:12,152 --> 00:51:15,614
Estás a ver? Ficou resolvido
com a minha oração sincera.

762
00:51:16,448 --> 00:51:17,700
